creator: The cousins
descriptionHtml:
History
In a world where the sky is both a sanctuary and a battleground, you are a brave bird fighting for survival. As he soars freely through the air, he witnesses the tragedy of fatal bird-plane collisions.

Determined to prevent further deaths and protect your species, you embark on a risky journey in search of a safe haven for the birds. Facing dangers such as strong winds and eager predators, you must utilize your flying skills and find allies along the way.

You meet other fighting birds who share your cause and together form an unlikely alliance. Each bird has unique abilities that will be essential to overcome the challenges and survive the dangers of the sky.

As you brave stormy flights, uncover secrets and avoid human planes, you uncover an ancient legend of a hidden haven for birds. The legend says that there the birds can live in peace and security, far from the dangers of human technology.

With renewed hope, you and your allies launch into one last thrilling battle against the elements and human interference. The fate of your species and the promise of a new beginning rest in your wings.

Get ready for a challenging and awe-inspiring journey where you'll have to fly high, show courage and strategy to protect your species and find your way to survival. Venture through the skies, gather allies and fight for the future of birds.

How to play:

1- The bird is guided by touching the screen.
2- Dodge the planes to not receive damage, if you receive the cell phone it will vibrate
3- Life hearts occasionally appear to increase your health, don't miss it! But be careful with planes.
4- If your life reaches zero the game ends and the highest score is recorded.
